The paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) tasks such as text categorization and query reformulation, which are typically covered under the arXiv sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL).
